      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be posting this, but it\u2019s time for this absolute gem to find a new home. I\u2019ve treated this beauty like a member of the family\u2014always kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed with love every single weekend. It\u2019s in truly stunning condition; it still has that fresh interior scent and the paint shines like a mirror. There\u2019s a tiny, tiny mark on the front bumper from a pebble, but you\u2019d honestly have to point it out for anyone to notice. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this is the one!",
