      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine example of the legendary E46 platform. This S54 powerplant screams to its 8,000 RPM redline with surgical precision, thanks to a meticulously calibrated VANOS system and recent valve clearance adjustment. The subframe has been fully reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014ensuring the chassis remains rigid under high lateral G-loads. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a lock-tight limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry has been optimized with refreshed bushings and dialed-in damping. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanical masterpiece maintained to an exacting standard. Zero parasitic losses, just raw, naturally aspirated performance.",
