      "description": "Slip into the driver\u2019s seat and let the world outside dissolve into a blur of elegance. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time capsule of refined engineering, draped in a deep, lustrous finish that mirrors the midnight sky. The interior greets you with the unmistakable, rich aroma of hand-stitched leather\u2014untouched by time and preserved with the utmost care. Every curve of its silhouette tells a story of prestige, while the engine hums with a quiet, confident power that promises to turn every mundane commute into a grand adventure. This is a rare opportunity to own a masterwork that feels as if it just rolled off the showroom floor, waiting for a driver who understands that true class never fades.",
